messages.message:
Brian
Are you going to Jim's reunion?
Are you still thinking about coming for Thanksgiving??

Brian
Yes!  But we haven't gotten a plane ticket yet.

Yes!! Were you guys ok in Susie's room?? Jim and Olena in Chas Friday--I've never met her.... Maybe they'll come for TG too??
Grandma plans on bar hopping with you and Colleen ONLY and I'm to entertain "the others ". Lol

Brian
LOL, how was the visit!?  Iga just got a letter from immigration, "You are deemed to be a Lawful Permanent Resident of the United States"!!!
We will book our tickets promptly, Susie's room was Excellent!  So excited!  I hope Jim comes for TG too, he can get a resort and we will go to the beach there ;D
